org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.escape

Class FI_EscapeSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.escape.FI_EscapeSummary

  • class FI_EscapeSummary
extends Object
    This class holds the results of a flow-insensitive escape analysis for a method.
